  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840020/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1763896980\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840020/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1763896980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840020/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1763896980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Experience the adrenaline rush of emergency response in Ambulance Chauffeur Simulator 2. Take the driver's seat of an ambulance and race against the clock to deliver doctors to critical accident scenes. Your decisions and skills will determine whether patients receive timely medical attention or face dire consequences.<br><br>Navigate bustling city streets and rugged mountain terrain, overcoming traffic and unpredictable obstacles. With every second crucial, precision driving is paramount. Each mission presents unique challenges, from weaving through urban traffic to tackling steep mountain passes.<br><br>Ambulance Chauffeur Simulator 2 offers a pulse-pounding experience, demanding quick thinking and daring maneuvers to save lives. Can you handle the pressure and make split-second decisions in the face of danger? Download now and test your mettle as an ambulance chauffeur!<br><br>Game Features:<br><br>- Drive 3 distinct ambulance models<br>- Conquer 10 challenging levels<br>- Race against the clock to save lives",
  "about_the_game": "Experience the adrenaline rush of emergency response in Ambulance Chauffeur Simulator 2. Take the driver's seat of an ambulance and race against the clock to deliver doctors to critical accident scenes. Your decisions and skills will determine whether patients receive timely medical attention or face dire consequences.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNavigate bustling city streets and rugged mountain terrain, overcoming traffic and unpredictable obstacles. With every second crucial, precision driving is paramount. Each mission presents unique challenges, from weaving through urban traffic to tackling steep mountain passes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAmbulance Chauffeur Simulator 2 offers a pulse-pounding experience, demanding quick thinking and daring maneuvers to save lives. Can you handle the pressure and make split-second decisions in the face of danger? Download now and test your mettle as an ambulance chauffeur!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame Features:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Drive 3 distinct ambulance models<br />\r\n- Conquer 10 challenging levels<br />\r\n- Race against the clock to save lives",
